name: CARTOGRAM
description:
Anamorphed map, guiding gif 
In a dream I felt twinspirits pale bird footsteps of night mutter guiding a way to execute the order  
omega wolf and her sister 
sharp rocks soft skin and breath in 
pixels are as wet as ink 
spitting their secrets 
and yet, only silence can spell 
the essence 
nfkey ancient link in the hash tree archaic whisper of communion the blocks must be moist from one heart to yours same old melody co.dependency 
rock by rock 
path to the genesis block
